OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FSunshine and showers Wednesday. Rain
OL,7,Fpushing eastwards Thursday, followed
OL,8,Fby sunshine and showers Friday.
OL,9,FStaying on the cool side, though
OL,10,Fturning a little warmer in the far
OL,11,Fsoutheast come Friday.
